{
  "texts": [
    "We populated the message history with the same reappraisal training that our human participants completed.",
    "We did not tailor the training language or structure for more effective prompting as we wanted to achieve fair comparison between humans and GPT.",
    "The only difference between the human and GPT reappraisal task instructions is that we added an extra sentence to keep reappraisals to a maximum of two sentences since the average length of human reappraisals was approximately 213 characters.",
    "This specification ensured relative reappraisal length equality between humans and GPT, since GPT naturally produced lengthier reappraisals than the human reappraisers in our sample.",
    "We initially tried to limit GPT reappraisal lengths by specifying a \"maximum token\", like word count, using the built-in parameter in the chat completion endpoint."
  ]
}